<riscos-prm>
<chapter title="Input examples">
<section title="Key input">
<p>
    <list>
        <item><p><input><key name='W'/></input> - the W key</p></item>
        <item><p><input><key name='ctrl'/><key name='X'/></input> - control and X (eg a cut)</p></item>
        <item><p><input><mouse name='select' repeat='2'/></input> - double click select (eg run a file)</p></item>
        <item><p><input><mouse name='select' action='drag'/></input> - drag select (eg making a selection)</p></item>
        <item><p><input><key name='shift'/><mouse name='select'/></input> - shift + select click (eg adding to a selection)</p></item>
        <item><p><input><key name='escape' repeat='2'/></input> - press escape twice (eg some special operation to get out of a system?)</p></item>
        <item><p><input><key name='shift'/><key name='ctrl'/><key name='f12'/></input> - shift + control + F12 (eg shutdown)</p></item>
    </list>
</p>

</section>

</chapter>

